2.5.42.name: wordpress/quizme
2.5.42.description:
This plugin is only supported on PHP 5.2 or greater.

QuizMe is an easy to use and easy to modify quiz system for WordPress. Written to be easy to use to none coders.

You can design many quizzes with an "easy" to use interface.

If you are having trouble and cannot find the answers in the FAQ you can post your support questions to the WordPress Support Forum

If you find QuizMe useful please rate it at wordpress.org and please consider making a donation to help us set aside more hours to maintain QuizMe

QuizMe is written by dcoda

You can check out our other plugins here

If you require a custom plugin yo
